<p>More tinkering and enhancements to some AutoHotKey scripts with WOWEE to allow some emacs keybindings throughout the realm of Windows.</p>
<figure><img src="https://emacs.dyerdwelling.family/ox-hugo/20240705073835-emacs--WOWEE-v0.3.3.jpg" width="100%">
</figure>

